{"title":"走远的牛","authors":["潘烽"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":5,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"走远的牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潘烽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在寒夜中走出  没有鞭声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四只脚卸去了许多沉重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以从未有过的急切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏冰又踏雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邀请太阳和春光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去寻找荒原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄绒绒的皮毛变成土地的色彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犄角不停地晃动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稳健地踩出深深的蹄窝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为身上承受着沉沉的负荷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热汗像雨滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿皮毛滑去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团团阴霾都让出路来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不希望有夜来临"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为对洒满阳光的土地爱得深沉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有草相伴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命便有了滋润"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}